Sure, here are some example sentences that use the Serbian word "dušo" in different forms and positions, with the starred word marked with an asterisk:

1. *Dušo*, jesi li videla gde sam ostavio ključeve? (Hey, darling, have you seen where I left the keys?)
2. Ovde je *dušo* najbolja hrana u gradu. (The best food in town is here, darling.)
3. *Dušo*, nemoj da se brineš, sve će biti u redu. (Sweetheart, don't worry, everything will be fine.)
4. Ne plači, *dušo*, nije tako strašno. (Don't cry, darling, it's not that bad.)
5. Kako si, *dušo*? (How are you, sweetheart?)
6. *Dušo* moja, hvala ti na svemu što činiš za mene. (My darling, thank you for everything you do for me.)
7. *Dušo*, dobro si to uradila! (Sweetheart, you did that well!)
8. Neću te zaboraviti, *dušo* moja. (I won't forget you, my darling.)
9. Mogu li da ti pomognem, *dušo*? (Can I help you, sweetheart?)
10. Uvek ću te voleti, *dušo* moja. (I will always love you, my darling.)

I hope this helps!